before detonation.

00:13:32.130 --> 00:13:34.000
- Lukrum's within hours
of reaching water.

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:36.700
- Space exploration is
where we solve problems that

00:13:36.700 --> 00:13:38.050
have never been solved before.

00:13:38.050 --> 00:13:39.720
- Are you OK with
what he's doing?

00:13:39.720 --> 00:13:40.424
