on everything.

00:13:49.246 --> 00:13:52.870
- [INAUDIBLE].

00:13:52.870 --> 00:13:55.959
- The future of humanity is
very much in the solar system.

00:13:55.959 --> 00:13:58.000
What kind of civilizations
are we going to build?

