00:29:35.340 --> 00:29:38.170
these sets were so
elaborate and so exacting

00:29:38.170 --> 00:29:41.620
because it allows the
actors to get into the role

00:29:41.620 --> 00:29:44.530
and really feel
like they're there.

00:29:44.530 --> 00:29:48.340
So we unfortunately lost
