00:29:51.480 --> 00:29:55.930
and many movies that you
think are British or American

00:29:55.930 --> 00:29:58.420
are actually made in
Budapest these days.

00:29:58.420 --> 00:30:01.420
And we're probably going
to move to Bucharest

00:30:01.420 --> 00:30:05.230
for the next season, if there's
a next season, because it's

00:30:05.230 --> 00:30:06.470
cheaper to make films there.

00:30:06.470 --> 00:30:10.600
But it's pretty elaborate
stuff, you know?

00:30:10.600 --> 00:30:14.290
It's the stuff of making
real movies as opposed

00:30:14.290 --> 00:30:15.830
to just a documentary series.

00:30:15.830 --> 00:30:18.340
So the investment in this
has been extraordinary.

00:30:18.340 --> 00:30:20.827
I think for the first
season, the sets were--

00:30:20.827 --> 00:30:22.660
there were $5 million
dollars worth of sets.

00:30:22.660 --> 00:30:25.150
And for the second season,
they added another $10 million

00:30:25.150 --> 00:30:26.010
for the sets.

00:30:26.010 --> 00:30:29.230
And the second season,
the sets are just huge

00:30:29.230 --> 00:30:31.680
compared to the first season.

00:30:31.680 --> 00:30:34.150
And I think if there's a
third and a fourth season,

00:30:34.150 --> 00:30:37.180
it will grow in that way.

00:30:37.180 --> 00:30:39.560
LEONARD DAVID: Who
